    "id00381_home:title:information" : "<h3><p>The platform will be operational from the day of the call until the day of the meeting.</p></h3><!--<p>Pursuant to the provisions of Article 539.2 of the restated text of the Companies Act, an Electronic Shareholder Forum is now available on the website of Dinamia, that both individual shareholders, as well as any voluntary associations they may create, can securely and privately have access to, as a means of facilitating and enhancing shareholder participation and communication during the period leading up to the Company’s General Meeting.</p><p>With regard to its access and use, shareholders must comply with the regulations of the Electronic Shareholder Forum, as approved by the Board of Directors, which are likewise available on Dinamia’s website.</p><p>To access and use the Forum you must create a new account and fill in the form with your personal details. You might access by digital certificate as well. In addition, you must be accredited as a shareholder.</p><p>This forum is moderated. Publication of the messages is open from Monday to Thursday from 09:00 a.m. to 07:00 p.m. and Friday from 09:00 a.m. to 03:00. p.m. Outside these hours no message will be published.</p><p>If you wish, through these links you can check Electronic Shareholder <a href=\"/bundles/lugh/workspace_base/Reglamento_en.pdf\" target=\"_blank\"><b>Forum Rules</b></a> and the list of <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"/home/images/CertificadosSoportados.pdf\"><b>issued certificates</b></a></p><p>Dinamia enables to its shareholders for this General Meeting  a contact mailbox :  <a href=\"mailto:junta2015@dinamia.es\">junta2015@dinamia.es</a></p>-->",
